# Agent 4 — Meta-Risk & Supervision Agent: Walkthrough

## What Was Built

The **Chief Risk Officer** of the pipeline — an independent auditor that scrutinizes Agent 3's allocation against market context and investor profile before it reaches the client. This is the "game changer" component that makes this a monster-level system.

### Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A1["Agent 1 Output<br/>(Regime, Vol, Risk)"] --> AUDIT["5 Independent<br/>Risk Audits"]
    A2["Agent 2 Output<br/>(Risk Score, Profile)"] --> AUDIT
    A3["Agent 3 Output<br/>(Proposed Allocation)"] --> AUDIT
    
    AUDIT --> |Pass/Warn/Fail| ADJ["Allocation Adjuster<br/>(Rebalancer)"]
    AUDIT --> |Findings| CRO["LLM Chief Risk Officer<br/>(Adjudicator)"]
    ADJ --> |Adjusted Weights| CRO
    
    CRO --> |APPROVED| OUT1["✓ Pass Through"]
    CRO --> |ADJUSTED| OUT2["⚠ Modified Allocation"]
    CRO --> |REJECTED| OUT3["✗ Must Reconstruct"]
```

### 5 Independent Risk Audits

| Audit | What It Checks | Key Metrics |
|-------|---------------|-------------|
| **Regime Consistency** | Allocation vs market regime rules | Per-regime equity/crypto caps, defensive floors |
| **Profile Alignment** | Allocation vs investor risk score/type | Behavioral type limits, liquidity requirements |
| **Drawdown Guardrails** | MC simulation vs investor tolerance | Median DD, P(loss), CVaR95, VaR95 |
| **Concentration** | Portfolio diversification adequacy | HHI index, risk contribution dominance |
| **Cross-Agent Coherence** | Contradictions between Agents 1/2/3 | Regime-strategy mismatch, consistency flags |

### Files Created (6 new, 1 modified)

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [agent4_output.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/schemas/agent4_output.py) | Pydantic schemas (audit results, adjusted allocation, CRO verdict) |
| [risk_auditor.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/ml/risk_auditor.py) | 5 independent audit submodules with regime-specific rules |
| [allocation_adjuster.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/ml/allocation_adjuster.py) | Regime-aware rebalancer with cap/floor constraints |
| [risk_adjudicator.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/llm/risk_adjudicator.py) | LLM CRO adjudicator with skeptical prompt + rule-based fallback |
| [agent4_supervisor.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/agents/agent4_supervisor.py) | Pipeline orchestrator with audit → adjust → verdict flow |
| [test_agent4.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/tests/test_agent4.py) | 26 comprehensive tests |
| [main.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/main.py) | Added `--agent 4` and `--agent3-json` CLI support |

