## How to Run

```bash
# Mock mode (intentionally bad allocation → tests all audits)
python main.py --agent 4 --mock

# Full 4-agent live pipeline
python main.py --agent 4 --agent1-json live_output.json --agent2-json agent2_live_output.json --agent3-json agent3_live_output.json

# Run tests
pytest tests/test_agent4.py -v
```

