# Agent 3 -- Quantitative Portfolio Strategist: Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A comprehensive quantitative portfolio strategist that leverages Agent 1 (Market Context) and Agent 2 (Investor Profile) to produce an optimal constrained allocation, stress-tested with 10,000 Monte Carlo scenarios, and explained via an institutional-quality LLM narrative.

### Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A1["Agent 1 Output<br/>(Regime, Vol, Risk)"] --> AU["Asset Universe Manager<br/>(Returns, Covariance)"]
    A2["Agent 2 Output<br/>(Risk Score, Max DD)"] --> AU
    
    AU --> |Expected Returns,<br/>Covariance, Bounds| PO["Portfolio Optimizer"]
    PO --> |Mean-Variance| STRAT["Strategy Selector"]
    PO --> |Risk Parity| STRAT
    PO --> |CVaR-Constrained| STRAT
    
    STRAT --> |Optimal Weights| MC["Monte Carlo Simulator<br/>(10,000 Scenarios)"]
    STRAT --> |Risk Decomp| METRICS["Portfolio Metrics"]
    
    MC --> |VaR, CVaR, P(Loss),<br/>Percentiles| OUT["Final Allocation Data"]
    METRICS --> OUT
    
    OUT --> EXPL["Allocation Explainer<br/>(LLM Layer)"]
    EXPL --> FINAL["Agent 3 JSON Output"]
```

### Key Capabilities

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| **Multi-Strategy Optimization** | Mean-Variance (Markowitz), Risk Parity (Equal Risk Contribution), CVaR-Constrained. |
| **Profile-Based Selection** | Automatically shifts strategy based on investor profile (`defensive`, `defensive_growth`, [balanced](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/tests/test_agent4.py#190-194), [growth](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/data/macro_data.py#280-321), `aggressive_growth`, `max_growth`). |
| **Monte Carlo Simulation** | Correlated Geometric Brownian Motion across 10,000 paths (252 forward days), tracking max drawdowns per path. |
| **Institutional Explanations** | Translates complex quant output into professional rationale with explicit trade-offs and guardrails via Gemini. |

### Files Created (6 new, 1 modified)

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [agent3_output.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/schemas/agent3_output.py) | Pydantic schemas (Allocation, Metrics, MC, Explanations, etc) |
| [asset_universe.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/ml/asset_universe.py) | 5-asset manager with regime-adjusted returns and stress-aware covariance |
| [portfolio_optimizer.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/ml/portfolio_optimizer.py) | Scipy constrained SLSQP optimization across 3 strat types + blending |
| [monte_carlo.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/ml/monte_carlo.py) | 10K-scenario GBM simulator |
| [allocation_explainer.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/llm/allocation_explainer.py) | LLM narrative generation with quant-only fallback |
| [agent3_strategist.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/agents/agent3_strategist.py) | Pipeline orchestrator with full logging |
| [test_agent3.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/tests/test_agent3.py) | 27 unit and integration tests |
| [main.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/main.py) | Added `--agent 3` support with `--agent1-json` and `--agent2-json` integration |

