# Agent 2 -- Cognitive & Behavioral Profiling Agent: Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A masterpiece-level Behavioral Finance Intelligence Agent that dynamically profiles investors through adaptive, scenario-based questioning calibrated to real market conditions from Agent 1.

### Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A1["Agent 1 Output<br/>(Regime, Vol, Risk)"] --> QC["Question Calibrator<br/>(ML)"]
    QC --> |stress_multiplier,<br/>categories| QG["Question Generator<br/>(LLM + Fallback Bank)"]
    QG --> Q["4 Adaptive Questions"]
    Q --> UA["User Answers"]
    UA --> BCA["Behavioral Consistency<br/>Analyzer (ML)"]
    UA --> RC["Adaptive Risk<br/>Classifier (ML)"]
    BCA --> |contradictions,<br/>biases, stability| OUT
    RC --> |risk_score,<br/>behavioral_type| OUT
    OUT --> LLM["LLM Narrative<br/>(Gemini)"]
    LLM --> FINAL["Agent 2 JSON Output"]
    FINAL --> A3["Agent 3 Input"]
```

### Key Capabilities

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| **10 Behavioral Biases** | loss_aversion, herd_behavior, anchoring, time_pressure, regret_aversion, overconfidence, recency_bias, disposition_effect, mental_accounting, sunk_cost |
| **8 Behavioral Types** | conservative_stable/anxious, moderate_balanced/volatile, growth_seeker (+vol sensitivity), aggressive_speculator/contrarian |
| **4 Stress Responses** | fight, flight, freeze, adapt |
| **3 Contradiction Types** | cross_question, stress_induced, anchoring |
| **Market-Adjusted Scoring** | Risk score modified by regime, vol, stability, stress response |

### Files Created (7 new + 1 modified)

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [agent2_output.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/schemas/agent2_output.py) | Pydantic schemas (2 phases) |
| [question_engine.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/ml/question_engine.py) | Stress calibration + category selection |
| [behavioral_analyzer.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/ml/behavioral_analyzer.py) | Contradiction & bias detection |
| [risk_classifier.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/ml/risk_classifier.py) | Continuous 0-1 risk scoring |
| [question_generator.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/llm/question_generator.py) | LLM generation + 8-question fallback bank |
| [agent2_daq.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/agents/agent2_daq.py) | Orchestrator with mock mode |
| [test_agent2.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/tests/test_agent2.py) | 23 tests |
| [main.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/main.py) | Added `--agent 2` support |

